line_2: Ye vivid tints of Persia's looms,

line_1: Belus forsakes his high frequented domes,
line_2: And o'er the famous plains of Shinah comes:

line_1: — Oft by her bubbling founts, and shadowy domes,
line_2: In gay undress the fairy legion roams,

line_1: From golden beds, and adamantine domes;
